n	margin-bottom: .5em;\n}\n\n@media screen and (min-width: 44.375em){\n.site-main > article {\n    margin-bottom: .1em;\n}\n}\n\n.post .entry-title{\n	font-weight: 400;\n	font-size: 1.5em;\n	text-decoration: underline;\ncolor:blueviolet;}\n\n.page-title{\ncolor: blue;\n	font-weight: 400;\n}\n\nsection#text-3.widget .widget-title{\n	color: white;\n  font-size: x-large;\n	background-color: blue;\n	margin:0px;\n	padding:10px;\n}\n\n.textwidget {\n    background-color:lightblue;\n	padding: 10px;\n}','twentysixteen-child','','inherit','closed','closed','','36-revision-v1','','','2018-11-15 16:33:06','2018-11-15 16:33:06','',36,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/15/36-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(330,1,'2018-11-15 16:35:51','2018-11-15 16:35:51','<p style=\"font-size: x-large; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\">綠色醫學</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: #339966;\"><strong>綠色醫學: 飲食療法+營養醫學+自然療法</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #339966;\">雙層功能: 預防疾病+治療疾病</span>  </strong></span></p>\r\n對於任何醫療，如果它不能使一個健康的細胞分裂成兩個健康的子細胞，那麼，它將無法治好所有的慢性病。細胞的複製能力是所有損傷和慢性疾病能夠復原的關鍵因素。\r\n\r\n一個細胞需要有足夠的電壓和原始材料，才能分裂成兩個健康的子細胞。\r\n\r\n綠色醫學: 探索和消除疾病的根本原因，針對人體健康細胞分裂所需的原材料和個人體質，採用正確的飲食和營養補充，消除阻礙健康的因素。使患者能夠恢復健康。\r\n<p style=\"font-size: x-large; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\">綠色健康檢查</span></p>\r\n檢查疾病的根本原因，而不是疾病的現象。它主要是根據飲食，生活方式，症狀或者血液，尿液，頭髮或糞便的樣本。下面是一些例子:\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\">體內荷爾蒙是否失衡:  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">例子有雌激素，黃體酮，睾酮，皮質醇，脫氫表雄酮等。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\">是否缺乏營養: <span style=\"color: #000000;\">例子有維生素D3，同半胱氨酸水平，B12，維生素C，硒，鎂，鋅等</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\">體內是否含有毒的重金屬: <span style=\"color: #000000;\">汞，鉛，鎘，砷，鋁等</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\">是否對某些食物過敏</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\">是否胃酸過少：<span style=\"color: #000000;\">與傳統思維相矛盾，</span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">胃酸過高是罕見的，可請醫生先測試你的胃酸。。</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">例</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">子有雌激素，黃體酮，睾酮，皮質醇，脫氫表雄酮等。</span></span>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2018-11-15 16:35:51','2018-11-15 16:35:51','',5,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/15/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(334,1,'2018-11-15 18:20:51','2018-11-15 18:20:51','p{\n	font-size: 1.5em;\n	margin: 0 0 1em;\n	line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\n.page .entry-title{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.site-branding .site-title a {\n    color: blue;\n	  font-weight: lighter;\n}\n\n.main-navigation a {\n	font-weight:normal;\n}\n\n.main-navigation .current-menu-item > a, .main-navigation .current-menu-ancestor > a {\n    font-weight: normal;\n}\n\n.entry-footer{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n@media screen and (min-width: 61.5625em){\n	body:not(.search-results) article:not(.type-page) .entry-content {\n		float: left;\n		width: 71.42857144%;\n	}\n\n}\n.entry-content{\n	float: left;\n}\n\n.category .entry-content{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.post{\n	margin-bottom: .5em;\n}\n\n@media screen and (min-width: 44.375em){\n.site-main > article {\n    margin-bottom: .1em;\n}\n}\n\n.post .entry-title{\n	font-weight: 400;\n	font-size: 1.5em;\n	text-decoration: underline;\ncolor:blueviolet;}\n\n.page-title{\ncolor: blue;\n	font-weight: 400;\n}\n\nsection#text-3.widget .widget-title{\n	color: white;\n  font-size: x-large;\n	background-color: blue;\n	margin:0px;\n	padding:10px;\n}\n\n.textwidget {\n    background-color:lightblue;\n	padding: 10px;\n}\n\n.cat-item{\n	font-size: larger;\n}','twentysixteen-child','','inherit','closed','closed','','36-revision-v1','','','2018-11-15 18:20:51','2018-11-15 18:20:51','',36,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/15/36-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(336,1,'2018-11-15 18:23:14','2018-11-15 18:23:14','<a href=\"../ca