closed','','14-revision-v1','','','2018-11-18 17:08:32','2018-11-18 17:08:32','',14,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/18/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(388,1,'2018-11-18 17:14:36','2018-11-18 17:14:36','<strong><span style=\"color: #800080; font-size: larger;\">消除便秘</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\"> 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration: underline;\">[基礎篇：健康飲食</span>]</span></strong></span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #008080;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></strong></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span></strong></span> :</span><img class=\"wp-image-443 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enema-bag-.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"199\" height=\"199\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: (如圖所示)灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個管嘴，肛門，和肛門內側。2. 在灌腸袋內裝入3至4杯乾淨水，將灌腸袋掛在高於身體的地方，鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出，關閉夾子。3.  身體平躺在地板上，將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，4.  5-10分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質]</span> </span></strong> :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 服用檸檬酸鎂</span>， <span style=\"color: #000000;\">鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助糞便通過腸道。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span></strong></span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。例子有蘆薈葉、鼠李皮(Cascara Sagrada bark)萃取 、番瀉葉(Senna leaf and pad)萃取、車前子、大黃根(rhubarb root )、辣椒。 諮詢可靠的中醫 。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080; font-size: larger;\"><strong>清除腸道毒素</strong></span>\r\n\r\n毒素粘合劑可以吸收大腸中的毒素，防止它被重新吸收到血液中。腸道毒素包括重金屬，殺蟲劑，除草劑，黃曲霉毒素(aflatoxin)和黴菌毒素(mycotoxin)。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #008000;\">毒素粘合劑</span></strong><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">: 綠藻，活性炭(activated charcoal)，膨潤土(bentonite clay)</span></span>\r\n綠藻: 粘合重金屬。\r\n活性炭: 粘合黴菌毒素和其他毒素。\r\n膨潤土: 粘合黃曲霉毒素和其他毒素。\r\n\r\n將活性炭（一至兩茶匙）和膨潤土（一至兩茶匙）混合在一杯水中，然後飲用，多喝水。。綠藻可以與解毒飲料(參考營養食譜)一起服用，或在其它時間服用。\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>[警示]：</strong></span>服用草藥時必須注意其來源，是有機的還是無機的，是否經過認證的“無重金屬”污染。</h3>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>','消除便秘和毒素黏合劑','','publish','closed','closed','','%e6%b6%88%e9%99%a4%e4%be%bf%e7%a7%98','','','2019-12-15 22:52:03','2019-12-15 22:52:03','',0,'http://54.241.45.216/?page_id=388',0,'page','',0),(389,1,'2018-11-18 17:14:36','2018-11-18 17:14:36','Thid is s teast','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-18 17:14:36','2018-11-18 17:14:36','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/18/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(390,1,'2018-11-18 17:15:25','2018-11-18 17:15:25','<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/category/diet/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />健康網</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/消除便秘/\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />消除便秘</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/archives/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />調理肝膽</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/archives/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" /></a><a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/archives/\">調理</a><a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/archives/\">腎膀胱</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','研究文章','','inherit','closed','closed','','14-revision-v1','','','2018-11-18 17:15:25','2018-11-18 17:15:25','',14,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/18/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(392,1,'2018-11-18 17:23:31','2018-11-18 17:23:31','p{\n	font-size: 1.4em;\n	margin: 0 0 1em;\n	line-height: 1.6em;\n}\n\n.page .entry-title{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.site-branding .site-title a {\n    color: blue;\n	  font-weight: lighter;\n}\n\n.main-navigation a {\n	font-weight:normal;\n}\n\n.main-navigation .current-menu-item > a, .main-navigation .current-menu-ancestor > a {\n    font-weight: normal;\n}\n\n.entry-footer{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n@media screen and (min-width: 61.5625em){\n	body:not(.search-results) article:not(.type-page) .entry-content {\n		float: left;\n		width: 71.42857144%;\n	}\n\n}\n.entry-content{\n	float: left;\n}\n\n.category .entry-content{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.post{\n	margin-bottom: .5em;\n}\n\n@media screen and (min-width: 44.375em){\n.site-main > article {\n    margin-bottom: .1em;\n}\n}\n\n.post .entry-title{\n	font-weight: 400;\n	font-size: 1.5em;\n	text-decoration: underline;\ncolor:blueviolet;}\n\n.page-title{\ncolor: blue;\n	font-weight: 400;\n}\n\nsection#text-5.widget .widget-title{\n	color: white;\n  font-size: x-large;\n	background-color: blue;\n	margin:0px;\n	padding:10px;\n}\n\n.textwidget {\n    background-color:lightblue;\n	padding: 1