	font-weight: 400;\n}\n\nsection#text-5.widget .widget-title{\n	color: white;\n  font-size: x-large;\n	background-color: blue;\n	margin:0px;\n	padding:10px;\n}\n\n.textwidget {\n    background-color:lightblue;\n	padding: 10px;\n}\n\n.cat-item{\n	font-size: larger;\n}\n\n.cat-item-23{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.lwa-username-label, .lwa-password-label{\n	width: 120px;\n}\n\n.site-branding{\n	margin-right: 8em;\n}\n\n.site-header-menu{\n	margin-top: 2em;\n}\n\n#post-16 .entry-content{\n	display: flex;\n	flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n\n#post-16 .entry-content p{\n	display:inline-block;\n	margin: .5em 1em;\n	width: 200px;\n}\n\n#post-14 .entry-content{\n	display: flex;\n	flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n\n#post-14 .entry-content p{\n	display:inline-block;\n	margin: 2em 1em;\n	width: 200px;\n	border: 2px solid black;\n	height: 200px;\n	text-decoration: none;\n}\n\n#post-14 .entry-content a {\n	box-shadow: none;\n}\n\n.page-id-14 section#categories-2 {\n    display: none;\n}\n\n.category-23 section#categories-2{\n	display: none;\n}','twentysixteen-child','','inherit','closed','closed','','36-revision-v1','','','2018-11-18 21:43:31','2018-11-18 21:43:31','',36,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/18/36-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(415,1,'2018-11-19 11:46:55','2018-11-19 11:46:55','代謝綜合徵(高血脂，高血壓，高血糖和肥胖)可能有一個相同的原因。如果此常見的原因可被確診和消除，所有的症狀將可以同時得到改善甚至痊癒。\r\n\r\n胰島素抗性是代謝綜合徵的早期原因。食用或飲用精製糖尤其是果糖，玉米糖漿，蔗糖和葡萄糖，升高的血糖會比從全食物中獲得的高很多。針對這種血糖的超負荷，胰腺必須分泌大量的胰島素，以幫助清除血液中多餘的糖。如果不調整飲食，血液持續超負荷的胰島素，會逐漸使細胞產生對胰島素的抗性，引起代謝綜合徵。\r\n\r\n這些不斷增加的胰島素水平會導致肝臟增加LDL（壞）膽固醇的生產，降低HDL（好）膽 固醇的生產。它們也促進腎臟保留鈉，或腎上腺分泌過多的腎上腺素，從而導致高血壓。最明顯的是，增加三甘油酯的合成（體細胞內的脂肪），造成肥胖。\r\n\r\n為了預防上述的健康問題，第一步是檢測胰島素抗性(除了正常的血糖測量)，或者叫糖耐量胰島素抗性檢測（glucose tolerance insulin resistance test , GT-IRT）。如果GT-IRT顯示有胰島素抗性，這意味著增加未來（甚至10年後）2型糖尿病的風險。','代謝綜合徵的原因: 胰島素抗性','','publish','open','open','','%e6%b2%bb%e7%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e8%ac%9d%e7%b6%9c%e5%90%88%e5%be%b5%e7%9a%84%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0-%e9%a3%b2%e9%a3%9f%e8%88%87%e7%87%9f%e9%a4%8a-nov-19-2018','','','2019-12-08 17:10:44','2019-12-08 17:10:44','',0,'http://54.241.45.216/?p=415',0,'post','',0),(416,1,'2018-11-19 11:46:55','2018-11-19 11:46:55','代謝綜合徵(高血脂，高血壓，高血糖和肥胖)可能有一個相同的原因。如果此常見的原因可被確診和消除，所有的症狀將可以同時得到改善甚至痊癒。不幸的是，西醫治療通常只是治標，而不是治療病因。因此，降膽固醇藥物被用來治療高膽固醇，降血壓藥被用於治療高血壓，以及降血糖藥用於治療糖尿病。患者（尤其是老年人），通常長期服用各種不同類型的藥物，藥物的副作用往往影響患者的生活質量，患者的健康也永遠得不到改善，除非患者主動徹底改善飲食和營養。\r\n\r\n胰島素抗性是高膽固醇，高血壓和肥胖的原因之一。胰島素抗性如果不治療，在未來會發展為2型糖尿病。西醫通常不檢測或者不知道如何檢測患者的胰島素抗性。\r\n\r\n食用或飲用精製糖尤其是果糖，玉米糖漿，蔗糖和葡萄糖，升高的血糖會比從全食物中獲得的高很多。針對這種血糖的超負荷，胰腺必須分泌大數量的胰島素，以幫助清除血液中多餘的糖。如果不調整飲食，血液持續超負荷的胰島素，會逐漸使細胞產生對胰島素的抗性，容易引起高血脂，高血壓，和肥胖，或者最終發展為糖尿病，無法控制血糖。\r\n\r\n對胰島素抗性和2型糖尿病有遺傳傾向的人，即使吃了太多的天然來源碳水化合物(穀物等)，也可能會有額外的胰島素抗性問題。\r\n\r\n這些不斷增加的胰島素水平可能會導致肝臟增加LDL（壞）膽固醇生產，降低HDL（好）膽固醇的生產。它們也可以促進腎臟保留鈉，或腎上腺分泌過多的腎上腺素，從而導致高血壓。最明顯的，精製糖或簡單碳水化合物的消耗和過量的胰島素分泌，通常導致增加三甘油酯的合成（體細胞內的脂肪），造成肥胖。\r\n\r\n為了防止和克服上述的健康問題，第一步是諮詢知道檢測胰島素抗性(除了正常的血糖測量) 的醫生，或者叫糖耐量胰島素抗性檢測（glucose tolerance insulin resistance test , GT-IRT）。如果GT-IRT顯示有胰島素抗性，這意味著增加未來（甚至10年後）2型糖尿病的風險。如果你有胰島素抗性，飲食避免一切精製糖和碳水化合物（例如澱粉）。吃健康的飲食有足夠的優質蛋白質和ω-3含量豐富的食物，適當的運動。補充下列營養成分或複合維生素和礦物質配方: 鉻，菸酸(niacin)，煙酰胺(Niacinamide)，生物素(Biotin)，α-硫辛酸(Alpha-lipoic acid)，輔酶，維生素K，D，維生素E，維生素C，鎂，釩，錳，並尋找一個良好的調節血糖配方，以上療法已被成功用於改善代謝綜合徵','治療代謝綜合徵的原因: 飲食與營養  Nov. 19, 2018','','inherit','closed','closed','','415-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 11:46:55','2018-11-19 11:46:55','',415,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(418,1,'2019-12-08 17:10:41','2019-12-08 17:10:41','代謝綜合徵(高血脂，高血壓，高血糖和肥胖)可能有一個相同的原因。如果此常見的原因可被確診和消除，所有的症狀將可以同時得到改善甚至痊癒。\n\n胰島素抗性是代謝綜合徵的早期原因。食用或飲用精製糖尤其是果糖，玉米糖漿，蔗糖和葡萄糖，升高的血糖會比從全食物中獲得的高很多。針對這種血糖的超負荷，胰腺必須分泌大量的胰島素，以幫助清除血液中多餘的糖。如果不調整飲食，血液持續超負荷的胰島素，會逐漸使細胞產生對胰島素的抗性，引起代謝綜合徵。\n\n這些不斷增加的胰島素水平會導致肝臟增加LDL（壞）膽固醇的生產，降低HDL（好）膽 固醇的生產。它們也促進腎臟保留鈉，或腎上腺分泌過多的腎上腺素，從而導致高血壓。最明顯的是，增加三甘油酯的合成（體細胞內的脂肪），造成肥胖。\n\n為了預防上述的健康問題，第一步是檢測胰島素抗性(除了正常的血糖測量)，或者叫糖耐量胰島素抗性檢測（glucose tolerance insulin resistance test , GT-IRT）。如果GT-IRT顯示有胰島素抗性，這意味著增加未來（甚至10年後）2型糖尿病的風險。','代謝綜合徵的原因: 胰島素抗性','','inherit','closed','closed','','415-autosave-v1','','','2019-12-08 17:10:41','2019-12-08 17:10:41','',415,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/415-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(419,1,'2018-11-19 11:53:14','2018-11-19 11:53:14','代謝綜合徵(高血脂，高血壓，高血糖和肥胖)可能有一個相同的原因。如果此常見的原因可被確診和消除，所有的症狀將可以同時得到改善甚至痊癒。不幸的是，西醫治療通常只是治標，而不是治療病因。因此，降膽固醇藥物被用來治療高膽固醇，降血壓藥被用於治療高血壓，以及降血糖藥用於治療糖尿病。患者（尤其是老年人），通常長期服用各種不同類型的藥物，藥物的副作用往往影響患者的生活質量，患者的健康也永遠得不到改善，除非患者主動徹底改善飲食和營養。\r\n\r\n胰島素抗性是高膽固醇，高血壓和肥胖的原因之一。胰島素抗性如果不治療，在未來會發展為2型糖尿病。西醫通常不檢測或者不知道如何檢測患者的胰島素抗性。\r\n\r\n食用或飲用精製糖尤其是果糖，玉米糖漿，蔗糖和葡萄糖，升高的血糖會比從全食物中獲得的高很多。針對這種血糖的超負荷，胰腺必須分泌大數量的胰島素，以幫助清除血液中多餘的糖。如果不調整飲食，血液持續超負荷的胰島素，會逐漸使細胞產生對胰島素的抗性，容易引起高血脂，高血壓，和肥胖，或者最終發展為糖尿病，無法控制血糖。\r\n\r\n對胰島素抗性和2型糖尿病有遺傳傾向的人，即使吃了太多的天然來源碳水化合物(穀物等)，也可能會有額外的胰島素抗性問題。\r\n\r\n這些不斷增加的胰島素水平可能會導致肝臟增加LDL（壞）膽固醇生產，降低HDL（好）膽固醇的生產。它們也可以促進腎臟保留鈉，或腎上腺分泌過多的腎上腺素，從而導致高血壓。最明顯的，精製糖或簡單碳水化合物的消耗和過量的胰島素分泌，通常導致增加三甘油酯的合成（體細胞內的脂肪），造成肥胖。\r\n\r\n為了防止和克服上述的健康問題，第一步是諮詢知道檢測胰島素抗性(除了正常的血糖測量) 的醫生，或者叫糖耐量胰島素抗性檢測（glucose tolerance insulin resistance test , GT-IRT）。如果GT-IRT顯示有胰島素抗性，這意味著增加未來（甚至10年後）2型糖尿病的風險。如果你有胰島素抗性，飲食避免一切精製糖和碳水化合物（例如澱粉）。吃健康的飲食有足夠的優質蛋白質和ω-3含量豐富的食物，適當的運動。補充下列營養成分或複合維生素和礦物質配方: 鉻，菸酸(niacin)，煙酰胺(Niacinamide)，生物素(Biotin)，α-硫辛酸(Alpha-lipoic acid)，輔酶，維生素K，D，維生素E，維生素C，鎂，釩，錳，並尋找一個良好的調節血糖配方，以上療法已被成功用於改善代謝綜合徵。','治療代謝綜合徵的原因: 飲食與營養  Nov. 19, 2018','','inherit','closed','closed','','415-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 11:53:14','2018-11-19 11:53:14','',415,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(420,1,'2018-11-19 12:06:33','2018-11-19 12:06:33','代謝綜合徵(高血脂，高血壓，高血糖和肥胖)可能有一個相同的原因。如果此常見的原因可被確診和消除，所有的症狀將可以同時得到改善甚至痊癒。不幸的是，西醫治療通常只是治標，而不是治療病因。因此，降膽固醇藥物被用來治療高膽固醇，降血壓藥被用於治療高血壓，以及降血糖藥用於治療糖尿病。患者（尤其是老年人），通常長期服用各種不同類型的藥物，藥物的副作用往往影響患者的生活質量，患者的健康也永遠得不到改善，除非患者主動徹底改善飲食和營養。\r\n\r\n胰島素抗性是高膽固醇，高血壓和肥胖的原因之一。胰島素抗性如果不治療，在未來會發展為2型糖尿病。西醫通常不檢測或者不知道如何檢測患者的胰島素抗性。\r\n\r\n食用或飲用精製糖尤其是果糖，玉米糖漿，蔗糖和葡萄糖，升高的血糖會比從全食物中獲得的高很多。針對這種血糖的超負荷，胰腺必須分泌大數量的胰島素，以幫助清除血液中多餘的糖。如果不調整飲食，血液持續超負荷的胰島素，會逐漸使細胞產生對胰島素的抗性，容易引起高血脂，高血壓，和肥胖，或者最終發展為糖尿病，無法控制血糖。\r\n\r\n對胰島素抗性和2型糖尿病有遺傳傾向的人，即使吃了太多的天然來源碳水化合物(穀物等)，也可能會有額外的胰島素抗性問題。\r\n\r\n這些不斷增加的胰島素水平可能會導致肝臟增加LDL（壞）膽固醇生產，降低HDL（好）膽固醇的生產。它們也可以促進腎臟保留鈉，或腎上腺分泌過多的腎上腺素，從而導致高血壓。最明顯的，精製糖或簡單碳水化合物的消耗和過量的胰島素分泌，通常導致增加三甘油酯的合成（體細胞內的脂肪），造成肥胖。\r\n\r\n為了防止和克服上述的健康問題，第一步是諮詢知道檢測胰島素抗性(除了正常的血糖測量) 的醫生，或者叫糖耐量胰島素抗性檢測（glucose tolerance insulin resistance test , GT-IRT）。如果GT-IRT顯示有胰島素抗性，這意味著增加未來（甚至10年後）2型糖尿病的風險。如果你有胰島素抗性，飲食避免一切精製糖和碳水化合物（例如澱粉）。吃健康的飲食有足夠的優質蛋白質和ω-3含量豐富的食物，適當的運動。補充下列營養成分或複合維生素和礦物質配方: 鉻，菸酸(niacin)，煙酰胺(Niacinamide)，生物素(Biotin)，α-硫辛酸(Alpha-lipoic acid)，輔酶，維生素K，D，維生素E，維生素C，鎂，釩，錳，並尋找一個良好的調節血糖配方，以上療法已被成功用於改善代謝綜合徵。','代謝綜合徵的原因: 胰島素抗性  Nov. 19, 2018','','inherit','closed','closed','','415-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 12:06:33','2018-11-19 12:06:33','',415,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(422,1,'2018-11-19 17:23:18','2018-11-19 17:23:18','<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和廢物，很容易重新吸收到血液，影響健康的恢復。</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 17:23:18','2018-11-19 17:23:18','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(423,1,'2018-11-19 17:25:00','2018-11-19 17:25:00','<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和廢物，很容易重新吸收到血液，影響健康的恢復。</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">THis is a test</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 17:25:00','2018-11-19 17:25:00','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(424,1,'2018-11-19 18:19:15','2018-11-19 18:19:15','<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #000080;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span>  :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4定期運動。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAvoid constipation promoting foods, Milk and dairy product,  bread, cookies, red meat, potatoes chip, deep frying, unripened green banana\r\n\r\nFoods that are high in prebiotic fiber include garlic, <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Health benefits and risks of onions\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/276714.php\">onions</a> and <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Benefits and health risks of bananas\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/271157.php\">bananas</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3705355/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">63</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Foods that contain prebiotic fibers can improve your digestive health and the balance of friendly bacteria in your gut. This can often help relieve constipation.\r\n<h2>11. Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 18:19:15','2018-11-19 18:19:15','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(425,1,'2018-11-19 18:20:22','2018-11-19 18:20:22','<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4定期運動。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAvoid constipation promoting foods, Milk and dairy product,  bread, cookies, red meat, potatoes chip, deep frying, unripened green banana\r\n\r\nFoods that are high in prebiotic fiber include garlic, <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Health benefits and risks of onions\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/276714.php\">onions</a> and <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Benefits and health risks of bananas\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/271157.php\">bananas</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3705355/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">63</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Foods that contain prebiotic fibers can improve your digestive health and the balance of friendly bacteria in your gut. This can often help relieve constipation.\r\n<h2>11. Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 18:20:22','2018-11-19 18:20:22','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(426,1,'2018-11-19 18:24:32','2018-11-19 18:24:32','<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生菌纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAvoid constipation promoting foods, Milk and dairy product,  bread, cookies, red meat, potatoes chip, deep frying, unripened green banana\r\n\r\nFoods that are high in prebiotic fiber include garlic, <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Health benefits and risks of onions\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/276714.php\">onions</a> and <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Benefits and health risks of bananas\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/271157.php\">bananas</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3705355/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">63</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Foods that contain prebiotic fibers can improve your digestive health and the balance of friendly bacteria in your gut. This can often help relieve constipation.\r\n<h2>11. Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 18:24:32','2018-11-19 18:24:32','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(427,1,'2018-11-19 18:52:02','2018-11-19 18:52:02','<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 18:52:02','2018-11-19 18:52:02','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(428,1,'2018-11-19 18:54:05','2018-11-19 18:54:05','<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 18:54:05','2018-11-19 18:54:05','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(429,1,'2018-11-19 18:56:04','2018-11-19 18:56:04','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 18:56:04','2018-11-19 18:56:04','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(430,1,'2018-11-19 18:59:15','2018-11-19 18:59:15','\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font:x-large\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 18:59:15','2018-11-19 18:59:15','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(431,1,'2018-11-19 19:00:15','2018-11-19 19:00:15','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font:x-large;text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 19:00:15','2018-11-19 19:00:15','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(432,1,'2018-11-19 21:25:45','2018-11-19 21:25:45','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">編輯的秘方</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 21:25:45','2018-11-19 21:25:45','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(433,1,'2018-11-19 21:54:14','2018-11-19 21:54:14','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong></span>：蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 21:54:14','2018-11-19 21:54:14','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(434,1,'2018-11-19 22:10:44','2018-11-19 22:10:44','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong></span>：蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> </span> :\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\