ber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 22:10:44','2018-11-19 22:10:44','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(435,1,'2018-11-19 22:13:47','2018-11-19 22:13:47','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span></strong> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span></strong>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800080;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong></span>：蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> </span></strong> :\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\">[灌腸器具]</span></strong>: 灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 22:13:47','2018-11-19 22:13:47','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(436,1,'2018-11-19 22:22:05','2018-11-19 22:22:05','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: 灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個肛門，和肛門內側。2. 將灌腸袋裝入3至4杯乾淨水。鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，幾分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 22:22:05','2018-11-19 22:22:05','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(437,1,'2018-11-19 22:26:55','2018-11-19 22:26:55','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: 灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個肛門，和肛門內側。2. 將灌腸袋裝入3至4杯乾淨水。鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，幾分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2>12. Eat prunes</h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"imageWidgetWrapper\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" alt=\"Prunes for constipation.\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/articles/318/318694/prunes-for-constipation.jpg\" data-sharing-image-index=\"4\" /></span>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_hover_text image-imageSharing\">\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button pinterest image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"pinterest\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button facebook image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"facebook\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"imageSharing_button twitter image-imageSharing sharrre\" data-targetwebsite=\"twitter\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPrunes and prune juice are often touted as nature\'s remedy for constipation - and for good reason.\r\n\r\nIn addition to fiber, prunes contain the natural laxative sorbitol. This is a sugar alcohol that has a laxative effect (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11401245\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">71</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24090144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72</a>).\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Studies have shown that prunes may be more effective than fiber. If you\'re constipated, prunes could be the easiest natural solution available (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">74</a>).</p>\r\nThe effective dose is thought to be around 50 grams (about 7 medium-sized prunes) twice a day (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21323688\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">73</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21643036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">75</a>).\r\n\r\nHowever, you may want to avoid prunes if you have IBS, as sugar alcohols are known FODMAPs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Prunes contain the sugar alcohol sorbitol, which has a laxative effect. Prunes can be a very effective remedy for constipation.\r\n<h2>13. Try avoiding dairy</h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 22:26:55','2018-11-19 22:26:55','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(438,1,'2018-11-19 22:51:03','2018-11-19 22:51:03','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: 灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個肛門，和肛門內側。2. 將灌腸袋裝入3至4杯乾淨水。鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，幾分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質] :</span> :  鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助大便通過腸道。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 22:51:03','2018-11-19 22:51:03','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(439,1,'2018-11-19 22:54:08','2018-11-19 22:54:08','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: 灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個肛門，和肛門內側。2. 將灌腸袋裝入3至4杯乾淨水。鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，幾分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質] </span> :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 服用檸檬酸鎂</span>， <span style=\"color: #000000;\">鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助糞便通過腸道。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2> Try magnesium citrate</h2>\r\n<p data-spx-slot=\"1\">Taking <a class=\"keywords\" title=\"Why do we need magnesium?\" href=\"https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/286839.php\">magnesium</a> citrate is a popular home remedy against constipation. It is a type of osmotic laxative that can be bought over-the-counter or <a class=\"is_affiliate_link\" href=\"http://amzn.to/2BO4JM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">online</a> (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2780140/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">69</a>).</p>\r\nTaking moderate amounts of magnesium supplements can help relieve constipation. Higher doses are sometimes used to prep and clean out the bowel before surgery or other medical procedures (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0011020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70</a>).\r\n\r\n<strong>Bottom line</strong>: Taking a magnesium citrate supplement can help against constipation. It is available over-the-counter.\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-19 22:54:08','2018-11-19 22:54:08','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/19/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(440,1,'2018-11-20 01:12:04','2018-11-20 01:12:04','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。combination of rhubarb root and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: 灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個肛門，和肛門內側。2. 將灌腸袋裝入3至4杯乾淨水。鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，幾分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質] </span> :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 服用檸檬酸鎂</span>， <span style=\"color: #000000;\">鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助糞便通過腸道。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。例子有蘆薈葉、鼠李皮(Cascara Sagrada bark) 、番瀉葉和豆莢(Senna leaf and pad)、辣椒。 諮詢可靠的中醫 。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 01:12:04','2018-11-20 01:12:04','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(441,1,'2018-11-20 01:14:43','2018-11-20 01:14:43','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。 and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: 灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個肛門，和肛門內側。2. 將灌腸袋裝入3至4杯乾淨水。鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，幾分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質] </span> :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 服用檸檬酸鎂</span>， <span style=\"color: #000000;\">鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助糞便通過腸道。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。例子有蘆薈葉、鼠李皮(Cascara Sagrada bark) 、番瀉葉和豆莢(Senna leaf and pad)、大黃根(rhubarb root )、辣椒。 諮詢可靠的中醫 。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 01:14:43','2018-11-20 01:14:43','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(443,1,'2018-11-20 01:36:39','2018-11-20 01:36:39','','enema bag','','inherit','open','closed','','enema-bag','','','2018-11-20 01:38:28','2018-11-20 01:38:28','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enema-bag-.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(444,1,'2018-11-20 01:38:58','2018-11-20 01:38:58','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。 and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: 灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-443\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enema-bag-.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"168\" height=\"168\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個肛門，和肛門內側。2. 將灌腸袋裝入3至4杯乾淨水。鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，幾分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質] </span> :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 服用檸檬酸鎂</span>， <span style=\"color: #000000;\">鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助糞便通過腸道。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。例子有蘆薈葉、鼠李皮(Cascara Sagrada bark) 、番瀉葉和豆莢(Senna leaf and pad)、大黃根(rhubarb root )、辣椒。 諮詢可靠的中醫 。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 01:38:58','2018-11-20 01:38:58','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(445,1,'2018-11-20 01:43:47','2018-11-20 01:43:47','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。 and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-443\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enema-bag-.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"136\" height=\"136\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: (如上圖所示)灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個肛門，和肛門內側。2. 將灌腸袋裝入3至4杯乾淨水。鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，幾分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質] </span> :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 服用檸檬酸鎂</span>， <span style=\"color: #000000;\">鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助糞便通過腸道。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。例子有蘆薈葉、鼠李皮(Cascara Sagrada bark) 、番瀉葉和豆莢(Senna leaf and pad)、大黃根(rhubarb root )、辣椒。 諮詢可靠的中醫 。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 01:43:47','2018-11-20 01:43:47','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(446,1,'2018-11-20 01:52:32','2018-11-20 01:52:32','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。 and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-443\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enema-bag-.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"136\" height=\"136\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: (如上圖所示)灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個管嘴，肛門，和肛門內側。2. 在灌腸袋內裝入3至4杯乾淨水，將灌腸袋掛在高於身體的地方，鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出。身體平躺在地板上，將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，5-10分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質] </span> :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 服用檸檬酸鎂</span>， <span style=\"color: #000000;\">鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助糞便通過腸道。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。例子有蘆薈葉、鼠李皮(Cascara Sagrada bark) 、番瀉葉和豆莢(Senna leaf and pad)、大黃根(rhubarb root )、辣椒。 諮詢可靠的中醫 。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 01:52:32','2018-11-20 01:52:32','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(447,1,'2018-11-20 01:56:11','2018-11-20 01:56:11','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。 and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[ 材料]</strong>：</span>蘆薈白膠，辣椒水（最辣的一種）或辣椒藥水。辣椒水: 將辣椒粉放入半杯熱水。   辣椒藥水: 用伏特加酒浸泡生辣椒（切碎）或辣椒粉一到兩週，然後將液體過出來。\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"> [方法] : </span></strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">將一些蘆薈膠敷在肛門周圍，並進入肛門內側，然後敷上辣椒水或辣椒藥水。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[水療灌腸]</span> :</span><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-443\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enema-bag-.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"136\" height=\"136\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[灌腸器具]</strong></span>: (如上圖所示)灌腸袋、導管、夾子(控制導管水流)、管嘴(供插入肛門)。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong> [方法]: 1.  </strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">利用橄欖油或凡士林，充分塗上整個管嘴，肛門，和肛門內側。2. 在灌腸袋內裝入3至4杯乾淨水，將灌腸袋掛在高於身體的地方，鬆開控制導管之夾子，讓管內之空氣流出，關閉夾子。3.  身體平躺在地板上，將管嘴左右搖動緩慢插入肛門，讓水流入肛門內，4.  5-10分鐘後，上馬桶將糞便排出。重複此動作2至3次，直至所排出的水呈清澈狀。</span><strong>\r\n</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[補充鎂質] </span> :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> 服用檸檬酸鎂</span>， <span style=\"color: #000000;\">鎂有助於放鬆消化道內的肌肉，加上它可以中和胃酸，幫助糞便通過腸道。</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[草本配方]</span> :  <span style=\"color: #000000;\">一些草藥有通便作用，可以幫助緩解便秘。例子有蘆薈葉、鼠李皮(Cascara Sagrada bark) 、番瀉葉和豆莢(Senna leaf and pad)、大黃根(rhubarb root )、辣椒。 諮詢可靠的中醫 。</span>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 01:56:11','2018-11-20 01:56:11','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(448,1,'2018-11-20 01:57:37','2018-11-20 01:57:37','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">消除便秘</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #003300;\">有便秘，必須消除。 便秘在大腸中積累毒素和過敏原，很容易重新吸收到血液，毒素和過敏原產生炎症，影響健康的恢復。 and cape aloe leaf </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">基礎篇：健康飲食</span> </span> :  1 多喝水或喝湯，2 多吃蔬菜，3 多吃可溶性纖維（浸泡車前子、亞麻籽或奇亞籽），4  多吃益生元纖維包括大蒜，洋蔥和香蕉，5  定期運動。\r\n\r\n不要吃易引起便秘的食物，例如:  牛奶和乳製品，柿子，麵包，餅乾，紅肉，薯片，油炸，生綠色香蕉。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[編輯的秘方]</span></span>： 以下秘方非常有效，可以很順利讓糞便排出來，但尚未對嚴重便秘患者進行試驗。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366