ttp://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/454-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(483,1,'2018-11-20 18:33:22','2018-11-20 18:33:22','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">調理肝膽</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[早晨飲料]</span>   </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[工具]</strong>：</span> 榨汁機，攪拌機\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[方法]</strong>：</span>1.  半杯胡蘿蔔汁     2.  半杯青蘋果汁或一杯紅甜菜根汁    3.   一到五瓣生蒜     4.  一至五湯匙橄欖油                 5.   ½茶匙磨碎的新鮮薑根\r\n\r\n將所有成分加一杯冷水置入攪拌機中混合。大蒜和橄欖油（1：1的比例）可以增加到個人的最大容忍量。為了節省時間，可榨更多的蔬果汁，並將剩餘的果汁保存在冰箱中供下次使用。','調理肝膽','','inherit','closed','closed','','454-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 18:33:22','2018-11-20 18:33:22','',454,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/454-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(484,1,'2018-11-20 18:46:24','2018-11-20 18:46:24','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">調理肝膽</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[早晨飲料]</span></span>   以下蔬果汁，喝五天。 然後，轉換到另一種飲料喝五天，保持輪流.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[工具]</strong>：</span> 榨汁機，攪拌機\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[方法]</strong>：</span>1.  半杯胡蘿蔔汁     2.  半杯青蘋果汁或一杯紅甜菜根汁    3.   一到五瓣生蒜     4.  一至五湯匙橄欖油                 5.   ½茶匙磨碎的新鮮薑根\r\n\r\n將所有成分加一杯冷水置入攪拌機中混合。大蒜和橄欖油可以每天逐漸增加到最大量(五瓣大蒜和五湯匙橄欖油)，或每天保持三瓣大蒜和三湯匙橄欖油的比例。。為了節省時間，可榨更多的蔬果汁，並將剩餘的果汁保存在冰箱中供下次使用。','調理肝膽','','inherit','closed','closed','','454-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 18:46:24','2018-11-20 18:46:24','',454,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/454-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(485,1,'2018-11-20 18:47:32','2018-11-20 18:47:32','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">調理腎膀胱</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[早晨飲料]</span> </span>  \r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[方法]</strong>：</span> 1.  二杯西瓜    2.  一個檸檬：擠汁    3.  一捏把或一茶匙辣椒粉(最辣的)\r\n\r\n將配料和一杯冷水加入攪拌機中混合（約30秒）。','調理腎膀胱','','inherit','closed','closed','','462-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 18:47:32','2018-11-20 18:47:32','',462,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/462-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(486,1,'2018-11-20 18:49:28','2018-11-20 18:49:28','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">調理腎膀胱</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[早晨飲料]</span></span>   以下蔬果汁，喝五天。 然後，轉換到另一種飲料喝五天\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[方法]</strong>：</span> 1.  二杯西瓜    2.  一個檸檬：擠汁    3.  一捏把或一茶匙辣椒粉(最辣的)\r\n\r\n將配料和一杯冷水加入攪拌機中混合（約30秒）。','調理腎膀胱','','inherit','closed','closed','','462-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 18:49:28','2018-11-20 18:49:28','',462,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/462-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(487,1,'2018-11-20 18:49:55','2018-11-20 18:49:55','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">調理腎膀胱</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[早晨飲料]</span></span>   以下蔬果汁，喝五天。 然後，轉換到另一種飲料喝五天。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[方法]</strong>：</span> 1.  二杯西瓜    2.  一個檸檬：擠汁    3.  一捏把或一茶匙辣椒粉(最辣的)\r\n\r\n將配料和一杯冷水加入攪拌機中混合（約30秒）。','調理腎膀胱','','inherit','closed','closed','','462-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 18:49:55','2018-11-20 18:49:55','',462,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/462-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(488,1,'2018-11-20 18:50:31','2018-11-20 18:50:31','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #003300; font: x-large; text-decoration: underline;\">調理腎膀胱</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[早晨飲料]</span></span>   以下蔬果汁，喝五天。 然後，轉換到另一種飲料喝五天。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[方法]</strong>：</span> 1.  二杯西瓜    2.  一個檸檬：擠汁    3.  一捏把或一茶匙辣椒粉(最辣的)\r\n\r\n將配料和一杯冷水加入攪拌機中混合。','調理腎膀胱','','inherit','closed','closed','','462-revision-v1','','','2018-11-20 18:50:31','2018-11-20 18:50:31','',462,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/20/462-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(489,1,'2018-11-21 01:02:25','2018-11-21 01:02:25','<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/category/健康網/\">     <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large; color: #003300;\"> 健 康 網</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/消除便秘/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large; color: #003300;\">消除便秘</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/調理肝膽/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />調理肝膽</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/調理腎膀胱/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />調理腎膀胱</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','研究文章','','inherit','closed','closed','','14-revision-v1','','','2018-11-21 01:02:25','2018-11-21 01:02:25','',14,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/21/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(490,1,'2018-11-21 01:04:38','2018-11-21 01:04:38','<span style=\"font-size: 1.4em; text-decoration: underline;\">抗炎飲料: 胡蘿蔔汁加薑黃</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-590 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_090044-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"184\" height=\"176\" />\r\n\r\n1/4杯切片胡蘿蔔（去皮）\r\n\r\n一根新鮮切片薑黃根（去皮）\r\n\r\n一片新鮮生薑根（去皮）\r\n\r\n一些黑胡椒粉\r\n\r\n將上述所有材料放入攪拌機中，加1杯水，攪拌1分鐘。根據個人舒適度，調整上述材料的用量。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"padding-top: 10px;font-size: 1.4em;text-decoration: underline;display: block;\">滋補飲料: 蘋果甜菜根生薑</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-589 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_085829-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"187\" height=\"172\" />\r\n\r\n一杯(約一個)切片青蘋果\r\n\r\n半杯切片生甜菜根（去皮）\r\n\r\n一茶匙鮮榨檸檬汁\r\n\r\n一片新鮮生薑根（去皮）\r\n\r\n1/8茶匙粗海鹽\r\n\r\n將所有成分放入攪拌機，加一杯冷水，攪拌1分鐘。\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"padding-top: 10px;font-size: 1.4em;text-decoration: underline;display: block;\">綠色營養飲料: 菠菜芒果加香菜\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-596 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_122646-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"187\" height=\"172\" />\r\n\r\n一杯新鮮菠菜\r\n\r\n一杯成熟的切片芒果\r\n\r\n一杯新鮮的 香菜或芫荽葉\r\n\r\n一茶匙鮮榨榨檸檬汁\r\n\r\n1/8茶匙粗海鹽\r\n\r\n將所有成分和一杯冷水加入攪拌機，攪拌一分鐘。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"padding-top: 20px;font-size: 1.4em;text-decoration: underline;display: block;\">雞肉洋蔥番茄湯</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-605 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_154821.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"189\" height=\"157\" />\r\n\r\n適量切塊有機雞肉（或深海魚）\r\n\r\n一個或兩個大洋蔥(切片)\r\n\r\n兩個或三個番茄(切片)\r\n\r\n一些海鹽\r\n\r\n洗雞肉，將它加水煮沸，然後將所有材料放入烹飪鍋中，可添加自己喜歡的材料。加水煮沸，然後用小火煮至少一個小時。吃前加入一些橄欖油。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','營養食譜','','publish','closed','closed','','blank-1','','','2019-12-12 01:04:00','2019-12-12 01:04:00','',0,'http://54.241.45.216/?page_id=490',0,'page','',0),(491,1,'2018-11-21 01:04:38','2018-11-21 01:04:38','','blank 1','','inherit','closed','closed','','490-revision-v1','','','2018-11-21 01:04:38','2018-11-21 01:04:38','',490,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/21/490-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(492,1,'2018-11-21 01:09:41','2018-11-21 01:09:41','<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/category/健康網/\">     <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large; color: #003300;\"> 健 康 網</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/消除便秘/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large; color: #003300;\">消除便秘</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/調理肝膽/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />調理肝膽</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/調理腎膀胱/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />調理腎膀胱</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/blank-1/\">Content\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','研究文章','','inherit','closed','closed','','14-revision-v1','','','2018-11-21 01:09:41','2018-11-21 01:09:41','',14,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/21/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(493,1,'2018-11-21 01:10:01','2018-11-21 01:10:01','<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/category/健康網/\">     <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large; color: #003300;\"> 健 康 網</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/消除便秘/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large; color: #003300;\">消除便秘</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/調理肝膽/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />調理肝膽</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/調理腎膀胱/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/diet.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"71\" height=\"72\" />調理腎膀胱</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/blank-1/\">Content</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','研究文章','','inherit','closed','closed','','14-revision-v1','','','2018-11-21 01:10:01','2018-11-21 01:10:01','',14,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/21/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(494,1,'2018-11-21 01:11:08','2018-11-21 01:11:08','<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span>流感的預防和營養療法</span></span></strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>飲食和生活方式</strong><strong>: </strong>. 足夠的睡眠 飲食避免簡單的碳水化合物（麵包，精製澱粉），糖抑制白細胞 定期做運動幫助壓力荷爾蒙正常化。\r\n\r\n<strong>維生素</strong><strong>D</strong><strong>: </strong><strong>對於成人每天</strong><strong>5,000 IU</strong><strong>的維生素</strong><strong>D</strong><strong>，對於兒童和嬰兒，典型的劑量是每天</strong><strong>2,000 IU</strong><strong>，與餐一起服用。</strong>. 超營養素可降低患流感症狀的風險。\r\n\r\n<strong>β</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>葡聚醣</strong><strong>Beta glucans:</strong> 使用補充酵母或蘑菇衍生的β葡聚醣<strong>，</strong>刺激第一道防禦免疫細胞，稱為巨噬細胞，減少上呼吸道感染的發生率。\r\n\r\n<strong>多吃大蒜和洋蔥</strong>。\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">流感營養療法</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>避免脫水，多喝水，電解質飲料和湯</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n2脈注射高劑量維生素C，一種強效流感治療方法，整體療法醫生可以提供幫助。\r\n\r\n3  接骨木萃取(<strong>Elderberry Extract): </strong><strong>抗感冒快速緩解症狀</strong>\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n 	<li><strong>抗流感市售的配方: </strong><strong>Anti-V Formula by Natural Factors, </strong><strong>可 在美國健康食品中找到</strong></li>\r\n</ol>','綠色療法','','publish','closed','closed','','%e7%b6%a0%e8%89%b2%e7%99%82%e6%b3%95','','','2018-11-21 16:40:06','2018-11-21 16:40:06','',0,'http://54.241.45.216/?page_id=494',0,'page','',0),(495,1,'2018-11-21 01:10:50','2018-11-21 01:10:50','','blank-2','','inherit','closed','closed','','494-revision-v1','','','2018-11-21 01:10:50','2018-11-21 01:10:50','',494,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/21/494-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(496,1,'2018-11-21 01:13:03','2018-11-21 01:13:03','<a href=\"http://54.241.45.216/category/健康網/\">     <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-175\" style=\"float: left;\" 