r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<div class=\"photobox_right\"></div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;','消除便秘','','inherit','closed','closed','','388-revision-v1','','','2018-11-21 03:05:07','2018-11-21 03:05:07','',388,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/21/388-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(514,1,'2018-11-21 03:06:40','2018-11-21 03:06:40','<span style=\"color: #008080;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[<strong>早晨飲料</strong>]</span></span>   以下蔬果汁，喝五天。 然後，轉換到另一種飲料喝五天，保持輪流.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[工具]</strong>：</span> 榨汁機，攪拌機\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[方法]</strong>：</span>1.  半杯胡蘿蔔汁     2.  半杯青蘋果汁或一杯紅甜菜根汁    3.   一到五瓣生蒜     4.  一至五湯匙橄欖油                 5.   ½茶匙磨碎的新鮮薑根\r\n\r\n將所有成分加一杯冷水置入攪拌機中混合。大蒜和橄欖油可以每天逐漸增加到最大量(五瓣大蒜和五湯匙橄欖油)，或每天保持三瓣大蒜和三湯匙橄欖油的比例。。為了節省時間，可榨更多的蔬果汁，並將剩餘的果汁保存在冰箱中供下次使用。','調理肝膽','','inherit','closed','closed','','454-revision-v1','','','2018-11-21 03:06:40','2018-11-21 03:06:40','',454,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/21/454-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(515,1,'2018-11-21 03:07:54','2018-11-21 03:07:54','<strong><span style=\"color: #008080;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[早晨飲料]</span></span> </strong>以下蔬果汁，喝五天。 然後，轉換到另一種飲料喝五天。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993366;\"><strong>[方法]</strong>：</span> 1.  二杯西瓜    2.  一個檸檬：擠汁    3.  一捏把或一茶匙辣椒粉(最辣的)\r\n\r\n將配料和一杯冷水加入攪拌機中混合。','調理腎膀胱','','inherit','closed','closed','','462-revision-v1','','','2018-11-21 03:07:54','2018-11-21 03:07:54','',462,'http://54.241.45.216/2018/11/21/462-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(517,1,'2018-11-21 03:16:56','2018-11-21 03:16:56','p{\n	font-size: 1.4em;\n	margin: 0 0 1em;\n	line-height: 1.6em;\n}\n\n.home .entry-title,\n.page-id-14 .entry-title,\n.page-id-16 .entry-title,\n.page-id-12 .entry-title,\n.page-id-10 .entry-title{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.entry-title{\n	  color: #003300;\n    font-size: 1.4em;\n    text-decoration: underline;\n	  text-ali