t-decoration: underline;\n}\n\na.glink span{\n	font-size: larger;\n	color: darkred;\n}\n#text-6 .widget-title{\n	font-size: 1.5em;\n	font-weight:600;\n	color: white;\n		background-color: darkblue;\n	padding:.1em\n}\n#text-6 .textwidget {\n	background-color: whitesmoke;\n	color:black;\n	font-weight:600;\n	padding: 0 2em;\n}\n\n#text-6 .textwidget p{\n	margin-bottom: .1em;\n}\n#text-6{\n	text-align:center;\n}\n\n.menu-item {\n    text-decoration: underline;\n    font-size: larger;\n    font-weight: 1000;\n}\n.menu-item a, a:active{\n}\n\n#gtranslate_wrapper{\n	margin-top: 15px;\n}\n\n#post-10 .entry-content span{\n	font-size: larger;\n}\n\n.page-id-14 .textwidget, .page-id-14 .widget-title\n{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.page-id-16 .textwidget,\n.page-id-16 .widget-title \n{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.page-id-18 .textwidget, .page-id-18 .widget-title\n{\n	display: none;\n}\n\n.home .textwidget{\n	background-color: white;\n}','twentysixteen-child','','inherit','closed','closed','','36-revision-v1','','','2019-12-08 23:38:04','2019-12-08 23:38:04','',36,'http://54.241.45.216/2019/12/08/36-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1160,1,'2019-12-12 00:27:08','2019-12-12 00:27:08','<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">綠色療法論壇: 分享個案<u></u><strong>，一起創造健康人生</strong></h3>\r\n[dwqa-submit-question-form]','分享論壇','','inherit','closed','closed','','16-revision-v1','','','2019-12-12 00:27:08','2019-12-12 00:27:08','',16,'http://54.241.45.216/2019/12/12/16-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1161,1,'2019-12-12 00:52:28','2019-12-12 00:52:28','<span style=\"font-size: 1.4em; text-decoration: underline;\">抗炎飲料: 胡蘿蔔汁加薑黃</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-590 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_090044-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"184\" height=\"176\" />\r\n\r\n1/4杯切片胡蘿蔔（去皮）\r\n\r\n一根新鮮切片薑黃根（去皮）\r\n\r\n一片新鮮生薑根（去皮）\r\n\r\n一些黑胡椒粉\r\n\r\n將上述所有材料放入攪拌機中，加1杯水，攪拌1分鐘。根據個人舒適度，調整上述材料的用量。\r\n&nbsp\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 1.4em; text-decoration: underline;\">滋補飲料: 蘋果甜菜根生薑</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-589 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_085829-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"187\" height=\"172\" />\r\n\r\n一杯(約一個)切片青蘋果\r\n\r\n半杯切片生甜菜根（去皮）\r\n\r\n一茶匙鮮榨檸檬汁\r\n\r\n一片新鮮生薑根（去皮）\r\n\r\n1/8茶匙粗海鹽\r\n\r\n將所有成分放入攪拌機，加一杯冷水，攪拌1分鐘。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 1.4em; text-decoration: underline;\">綠色營養飲料: 菠菜芒果加香菜\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-596 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_122646-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"187\" height=\"172\" />\r\n\r\n一杯新鮮菠菜\r\n\r\n一杯成熟的切片芒果\r\n\r\n一杯新鮮的 香菜或芫荽葉\r\n\r\n一茶匙鮮榨榨檸檬汁\r\n\r\n1/8茶匙粗海鹽\r\n\r\n將所有成分和一杯冷水加入攪拌機，攪拌一分鐘。\r\n&nbsp\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 1.4em; text-decoration: underline;\">雞肉洋蔥番茄湯</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-605 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_154821.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"189\" height=\"157\" />\r\n\r\n適量切塊有機雞肉（或深海魚）\r\n\r\n一個或兩個大洋蔥(切片)\r\n\r\n兩個或三個番茄(切片)\r\n\r\n一些海鹽\r\n\r\n洗雞肉，將它加水煮沸，然後將所有材料放入烹飪鍋中，可添加自己喜歡的材料。加水煮沸，然後用小火煮至少一個小時。吃前加入一些橄欖油。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 1.4em; text-decoration: underline;\">解毒飲料(重金屬螯合劑)</span>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #993366;\">[材料]:\r\n</span></strong>\r\n\r\n香菜(芫荽)，綠藻（粉末），β-丙氨酸Beta Alanine（粉末），維生素C（粉末），MSM（粉末）或苜蓿（粉末），加上一粒N-乙酰半胱氨酸NAC（每粒1000mg）。\r\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #993366;\">[方法]:</span></strong>\r\n將一些新鮮香菜放入攪拌機中，加入一杯或1 1/2杯過濾水，攪拌30秒，然後加入一湯匙β-丙氨酸和其餘粉末各1茶匙（或更多)，然後與NAC一起喝下此飲料。每天早上和下午準備一次。飲用後10分鐘，清除腸道毒素(參考大腸解毒)。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','營養食譜','','inherit','closed','closed','','490-revision-v1','','','2019-12-12 00:52:28','2019-12-12 00:52:28','',490,'http://54.241.45.216/2019/12/12/490-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1162,1,'2019-12-12 00:54:48','2019-12-12 00:54:48','<span style=\"font-size: 1.4em; text-decoration: underline;\">抗炎飲料: 胡蘿蔔汁加薑黃</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-590 alignleft\" src=\"http://54.241.45.216/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20181125_090044-2